<P>__{(confident)}
<D>__{oh, i am gonna talk to my sister.}
<C>__{kristoff}
<D>__{that's your plan? my ice business is riding on you talking to your sister.}
<C>__{anna}
<D>__{yup.}
<A>__{kristoff, so stunned by her casual plan, doesn't look where he's going and ends up with an ice spike to the nose. he stops short, gulp, moves carefully around the spike.}
